{"title":"枣园的灯光","authors":["孙学林"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣园的灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙学林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我常常想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那该是怎样的一盏烛火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腥风血雨扑不灭它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石派了数十万之众"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没能晃动它的焰心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那火焰依然热烈地跳动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛一枚旭日的精灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来它把数千年粘稠的夜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝作了一汪燃烧的灯油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有黑暗它在哪里燃得更欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到把旧中国的夜色熬干"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}